    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy. The engine currently runs but exhibits a persistent knock, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. The exterior shows substantial rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling across most surfaces. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and the air conditioning is non-functional. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, sold as-is.",
