      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a preserved dream. This isn't merely a vehicle; it's a rolling masterpiece that captures the very essence of a golden era. The coachwork glows with a depth that rivals a midnight sea, while the cabin offers a sanctuary of pristine leather and polished accents that feel as though they\u2019ve never known the touch of time. To turn the key is to awaken a symphony of precision, a mechanical heartbeat that yearns for the open road. This is a rare chance to own a legend that has been kept in a state of absolute grace, waiting for a driver who understands that some things are truly timeless.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
